metadata.name: Unravel People's VALHALLA
metadata.description: Abbreviation for unravel people's VALHALLA, which represents an inactive state of pVALHALLA. User can participate in a new VALHALLA acquirement subscription and will receive unravel people's VALHALLA as credit. upVALHALLA can be claimed into pVALHALLA when the subscription successfully acquires a new VALHALLA.
